{"tid":1360053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"‎[遍地開花] 到我地環保署做野啦","createTime":"2019-07-24T09:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T10:20:57.000Z","uid":148696,"like":217,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"87d67cee48524c82c02693a2c756d276a54b9558","tid":1360053,"uid":148696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:18:37.000Z","msg":"致 香港市民：<br />\n<br />\n此公開信是由來自環境保護署 (環保署) 職員發出。雖然我們並不是紀律部隊，但同為政府部門，我們堅信，公職人員應以服務市民、保護市民為宗旨。<br />\n<br />\n近日於元朗站發生的無差別襲擊事件，我們深感憤怒和痛心，對施襲者予以最嚴厲的譴責。對於警方拖延及選擇性執法，並不斷推卸責任，我們表示極度不滿，同為公職人員亦感羞恥。<br />\n<br />\n我們在此要求政府正面回應香港市民五大訴求；警方公平公正、不偏不倚地履行職務。<br />\n<br />\n我們環境保護署職員與香港人同行，共同為香港的自由民主奮鬥。<br />\n<br />\n一班關心社會的環境保護署公務員上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gnx41OB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGnx41OB.jpg&h=d28810d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33c7c969835b578e53f6a61885a15a965a885ac3","tid":1360053,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:21:26.000Z","msg":"多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8fd2b94a918b8375da5b94d57df7bce0959059","tid":1360053,"uid":124837,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:22:37.000Z","msg":"遍地開花 感謝你地嘅付出<br />\n希望上到街見到你地"},{"pid":"115373d0a7787a54900dda1043ccd2ec0c4f79a9","tid":1360053,"uid":81008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:24:00.000Z","msg":"又有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ff6a263419fc315e4ad650a4fb745a8c2707d4","tid":1360053,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:24:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a637c18a94e45013eda1dc0a4dad2b7a43471833","tid":1360053,"uid":148783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci